- Crisis event impact areas
- Territory control scoring

## Player Stats
- Health (0-20)
- Energy (scales 1-10 per turn)
- Momentum (0-5, generated through combat)
- Faction alignment affecting resource generation

## Game State
- Three-phase turn system (Deploy/Action/End)
- Crisis event countdown and effects
- Card synergy tracking via Data-Link
- Zone control state
- Resource pool management

## Combat Resolution
- Position-based damage calculation
- Zone control multipliers
- Crisis event modifiers
- Faction synergy bonuses

